2015年12月22日[[联合国大会|联合国大会]]根据大会第A/RES/70/212号决议，宣布每年2月11日为'''妇女和女童参与科学国际日'''（{{lang-en|International Day of Women and Girls in Science}}）<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://undocs.org/A/RES/70/212|title=A/RES/70/212 - E - A/RES/70/212|website=undocs.org|access-date=2019-10-25|archive-date=2019-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190603183501/https://undocs.org/A/RES/70/212|dead-url=no}}</ref> 这个节日表彰妇女在科学技术上的重要作用。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.un.org/en/events/women-and-girls-in-science-day/index.shtml|title=International Day of Women and Girls in Science, 11 February|website=www.un.org|language=EN|access-date=2019-10-25|archive-date=2020-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202204951/https://www.un.org/en/events/women-and-girls-in-science-day/index.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

